{"prayers":[{"phelps":"BH10505","text":"## Shoshone\n\nDA-MEH UPEH, DA-MEH UPEH,\n\nSEMES DA-NEH-MEH-NEH HA BEYUH MEH, DEAS MA-DE-ZA-POING DA BE-YAH NA-HA-NEE-DOH SOO- WI-KH DA-MEH UPEH DE-NEE TA GWAP DEAS DA DE-NEE-TA-GWAP KOOPH NAHK. MA DE DE-MA-ZI, UPEH, SU-KA MA-DEH HA-NEE DOH, DEAS GU-TA MA DEH M-EH SOO-NEEK SEE-DEH U-MA-BEE-ZA-KHON-DOH. DAMEH UPEH. GA DEAS MA-DEH ZA-PEH-TINDH, MA-DEH-DAH-TI-GEEK, MA-DEH NA-SOO BA-DU KHAN DOH, SOO-KA DA-NA-BOO-IPH. DEAS MA-DEH BE-YUH ZA-NEE-SHOON-GAH, MA-DEH GA-ME-NGH.\n\nO my God! O my God! Unite the hearts of Thy servants, and reveal to them Thy great purpose. May they follow Thy commandments and abide in Thy law. Help them, O God, in their endeavour, and grant them strength to serve Thee.  O God! Leave them not to themselves, but guide their steps by the light of Thy knowledge, and cheer their hearts by Thy love. Verily, Thou art their helper and their Lord.","name":"Shoshone","category":"Shoshone","order_in_cat":1,"source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"8bf3298a-77ef-4932-97b9-47f8c7a72849","v":"8a9u7zq736t1wyr3hyteb2r0p","notes":"Theory: Shoshone prayer 1 (section header: Shoshone). Opening: \"DA-MEH UPEH, DA-MEH UPEH, SEMES DA-NEH-MEH-NEH HA BEYUH MEH...\" No English translation available. Challenge: Shoshone transcription in non-standard format; critically endangered language.","book":"nai-US:bpnet","book_cats":{"bn:bpnet":{"cat":"একতার জন্য প্রার্থনা","order_in_cat":1},"bs:bpnet":{"cat":"Jedinstvo","order_in_cat":1},"ch:bpnet":{"cat":"OTRO SIHA NA TINAITAI","order_in_cat":2},"co:bpnet":{"cat":"Unita","order_in_cat":1},"cs:bpnet":{"cat":"Jednota","order_in_cat":1},"cy:bpnet":{"cat":"Unity","order_in_cat":3},"da:bpnet":{"cat":"Enhed","order_in_cat":1},"dgz:bpnet":{"cat":"Baigan U’uraewa (Unity)","order_in_cat":1},"el:bpnet":{"cat":"ΕΝΟΤΗΤΑΣ","order_in_cat":1},"en:bpnet":{"cat":"Unity","order_in_cat":1},"eo:bel-malnova":{"cat":"Bahá'u'lláh","cat_order":2,"order_in_cat":18},"eo:bpnet":{"cat":"Unueco kaj Paco","order_in_cat":